        "question": "数列 $\\{a_{n}\\}$ 满足：$a_{1} = a_{2} = a_{3} = 1$。令 $b_{n} = a_{n} + a_{n+1} + a_{n+2}$ ($n \\in \\mathbb{N}^{*}$)。若 $\\{b_{n}\\}$ 是公比为3的等比数列，求 $a_{100}$ 的值。",
        "solution": [
            "由条件知 $b_{n} = b_{1} \\cdot 3^{n-1} = 3^{n}$ ($n \\in \\mathbb{N}^{*}$)",
            "因此，$a_{n+3} - a_{n} = b_{n+1} - b_{n} = 3^{n+1} - 3^{n} = 2 \\cdot 3^{n}$ ($n \\in \\mathbb{N}^{*}$)",
            "于是",
            "$a_{100} = a_{1} + \\sum_{k=1}^{33}(a_{3k+1} - a_{3k-2}) = 1 + \\sum_{k=1}^{33}2 \\cdot 3^{3k-2}$",
            "$= 1 + 6 \\cdot \\frac{27^{33} - 1}{27 - 1} = 1 + \\frac{3}{13}(3^{99} - 1) = \\frac{3^{100} + 10}{13}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{3^{100} + 10}{13}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
